    <item>
      <title>美国就业岗位空缺数据疲软证实全球债券市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/rate-cut-hopes-are-galvanizing-demand-for-bonds-everywhere</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，全球债券市场涨势加速，美国就业岗位减少幅度超预期，导致美国国债收益率进一步下跌，表明全球最大经济体的经济正在降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/rate-cut-hopes-are-galvanizing-demand-for-bonds-everywhere</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 02:55:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
